snippet.title: Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp:The Respondent: The 6 Silver Bullets & Magic Ballistics of Family Law War
snippet.description:
It's well established that men kill themselves much more than women after divorce. Everyday in America 10 divorced men take their own lives. One of the main causes is our biased family law system.

In Episode 3 of my video podcast - The Respondent - #MenToo pioneer and men's rights activist Bettina Arndt joins me. We discuss how modern feminism is destroying so much of our society and culture.

Janice Fiamengo joins for a live Q&A after the episode. This all kicks off on Sunday, July 19th, at 1:00 p.m. Pacific Time on thinkspot. Register here: https://www.thinkspot.com/event_signup?event=NQuxyP
